<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title> Class Recording Slot Booking</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f3f6fa;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 25px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h3 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #222;
    }

    label {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      display: block;
    }

    input, select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #cfd7e3;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      outline: none;
      background: #fafbff;
    }

    input:focus, select:focus {
      border-color: #1d75d8;
      background: #fff;
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #1d75d8;
      border: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: #0f5fb8;
    }

    .message-box {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      white-space: pre-line;
    }

    .error-box {
      background: #ffe6e6;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff4b4b;
      color: #a30000;
    }

    .success-box {
      background: #e6ffe9;
      border-left: 4px solid #2ecc71;
      color: #0a7a33;
    }

    .report-link {
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .report-link a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #1d75d8;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .report-link a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Guidelines Box */
    .guidelines {
      background: #f7f9ff;
      border: 1px solid #d8e4f7;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .guidelines h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #1d75d8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .guidelines ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
    }

    .guidelines li {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container">

  <h3>Class Recording - Slot Booking Form</h3>

  <% if (message) { %>
    <div class="message-box <%= message.type === 'error' ? 'error-box' : 'success-box' %>">
      <%= message.text %>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <form method="post" action="/book">

    <label>Date</label>
    <input type="date" name="date" id="dateField" required>

    <label>Teacher Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="teacher" required>

    <label>Class Name(Venue)</label>
    <input type="text" name="className" required>

    <label>Mobile Number</label>
    <input type="text" name="mobile" required>

    <label>Subject</label>
    <input type="text" name="subject" required>

    <label>Period & Time</label>
    <select name="period" required>
      <% for (let p in periods) { %>
        <option value="<%= p %>"><%= p %> — <%= periods[p] %></option>
      <% } %>
    </select>

    <button type="submit">Book Slot</button>
  </form>

  <div class="report-link">
    <a href="/report">View Date-wise Report</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Guidelines Section -->
  <div class="guidelines">
    <h4>Booking Instructions</h4>

    <ul>
      <li>Select the correct <b>Date</b>, <b>Period</b>, <b>Subject</b> and <b>Class/Venue</b>.</li>
      <li>Ensure your <b>Mobile Number</b> is correct for communication purposes.</li>
      <li>Once submitted, your slot is confirmed immediately if available.</li>
      <li>If a slot is blocked by another teacher, the system will show details instantly.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Slot Blocking Policy</h4>
    <p style="font-size:13px; margin-bottom:6px;">When a period is booked, these periods become unavailable automatically:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><b>1st</b> → blocks 1 & 2</li>
      <li><b>2nd</b> → blocks 1, 2 & 3</li>
      <li><b>3rd</b> → blocks 2 & 3</li>
      <li><b>4th</b> → blocks 4 & 5</li>
      <li><b>5th</b> → blocks 4, 5 & 6</li>
      <li><b>6th</b> → blocks 5 & 6</li>
      <li><b>7th</b> → blocks 7 & 8</li>
      <li><b>8th</b> → blocks 7, 8 & 9</li>
      <li><b>9th</b> → blocks 8 & 9</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Examples</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>If <b>Period 2</b> is booked → <b>Periods 1, 2, 3</b> are blocked.</li>
      <li>If <b>Period 5</b> is booked → <b>Periods 4, 5, 6</b> are blocked.</li>
      <li>If <b>Period 9</b> is booked → <b>Periods 8 & 9</b> are blocked.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Note</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Blocking rules prevent clashes and ensure smooth scheduling.</li>
      <li>For issues, contact the system administrator.</li>
    </ul>

  </div>

</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<!-- Disable past dates -->
<script>
  const today = new Date().toISOString().split("T")[0];
  document.getElementById("dateField").setAttribute("min", today);
</script>

</body>
</html>
